body:
$!You can take the official practice car theory tests online for free.$!

There are 2 examples of the theory test you can practice online. You can't practise the hazard perception part with these tests.

The practice test screens look similar to the theory test you'll take at the test centre.

[Car driving theory test: example 1.](http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_187178.htm "Take car practice theory test example 1"){:rel="external"} 

[Car driving theory test: example 2.](http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_187179.htm "Take car practice theory test example 2"){:rel="external"}
